# MISC::IS_FRONTEND_FADING

## Summary
Only returns FALSE if no frontend fade is running

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
This function is hard-coded to always return 0.
